{
  "version": 1,
  "description": "Routing index for the SDD knowledge layer. Maps engineering areas (by file globs and keywords) to typed SDD references. Contains NO duplicated content — sdd_context.py resolves refs by slicing the live SDD/*.md files, so the harness can never drift stale from the design record. Ref grammar: ad:AD-xxx | nfr:NFR-xxx | uc:UC-xxx | risk:Rn | issue:In | sc:SCn | assume:An | sec:N.N (chapter section) | ch:NN (whole chapter, manual use).",
